<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/favicon.png">
    <title>Craftomania | Форум</title>

    <meta property="og:title" content="Craftomania | Форум" />
    <meta property="og:description"
        content="Форум майнкрафт для поиска игроков, команды, пати. Майнкрафт форум для того, чтобы создать свой сервер майнкрафт." />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://craftomania.net/img/favicon-alt.png" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://forum.craftomania.net/manuals/" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />

    <link href="https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/tt-norms-pro" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen" href="https://fontlibrary.org//face/tt-norms-medium" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://kit.fontawesome.com/7a9092486b.css" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" media="screen,projection">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap-grid.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #fff;
            background: url('../img/cloud-bg.png') repeat-x 0 / 90% auto;
            animation: cloud-bg 60s linear infinite;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: auto;
        }

        @keyframes cloud-bg {
            0% {
                background-position: 0 -100px;
            }

            100% {
                background-position: 100vw -100px;
            }
        }

        nav {
            position: relative;
        }

        nav .navbar {
            height: 95px;
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding-left: 30px;
            padding-right: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        nav .navbar .logo {
            margin-top: 27px;
        }

        nav .navbar .logo a {
            color: #000;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            text-transform: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        nav .navbar .logo a .forum {
            color: #bdbdbe;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        nav .navbar .search {
            height: 50px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            box-shadow: 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding-left: 10px;
            padding-right: 10px;
            margin-top: 22.5px;
            margin-right: 14px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        nav .navbar .search input {
            min-width: 200px;
            height: 29.34px;
            border-radius: 6px 0 0 6px;
            border: 1.5px solid #e2e2e2;
            font-family: "Nunito", sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            vertical-align: top;
            padding: 0;
            padding-left: 8px;
            padding-right: 8px;
            margin-top: 9px;
        }

        nav .navbar .search input:focus {
            outline: none;
        }

        nav .navbar .search input::placeholder {
            color: #b6b6b6;
        }

        nav .navbar .search button {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            position: relative;
            background: #11B2FF;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
            border: none;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-top: 9px;
            margin-left: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        nav .navbar .search button i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #fff;
        }

        nav .navbar .auth .auth-button {
            width: 150px;
            height: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(98.44deg, #8DEBFF 0%, #00ABFF 100%), #339DFF;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
            font-size: 19px;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'TTNormsMedium';
            font-size: 19px;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            margin-top: 22.5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        nav .navbar .auth .auth-button-mobile {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            position: relative;
            background: linear-gradient(98.44deg, #8DEBFF 0%, #00ABFF 100%), #339DFF;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
            font-size: 19px;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 22.5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        nav .navbar .auth .auth-button-mobile i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        .card {
            min-height: 600px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: #F3F7FC;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            padding-right: 25px;
            padding-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .topic-add i {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        .topic {
            width: 55%;
            position: absolute;
            top: 45%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background: #fff;
            background-size: 400px;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            padding-left: 30px;
            padding-right: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .topic .avatar {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            position: relative;
            background: #11B2FF;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .topic .avatar i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        .topic .title-subtitle {
            position: relative;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .topic .title {
            color: #3A4E57;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 25px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: -3px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .topic .subtitle {
            color: #959595;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 23px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        @media (max-width: 575.98px) {
            nav .navbar {
                padding-left: 25px;
                padding-right: 25px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

            nav .navbar .logo {
                margin-top: 15.5px;
            }

            nav .navbar .logo a .forum {
                font-weight: 600;
            }
        }
    </style>

    <nav>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                    <div class="logo">
                        <a href="/">Craftomania<br class="d-block d-sm-none"><span class="d-none d-sm-inline-flex"
                                style="color: #bdbdbe; font-weight: 500;">｜</span><span class="forum">ФОРУМ</span></a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="d-none d-lg-inline-flex search">
                            <form>
                                <input name="search" type="text" placeholder="Мини-игры">
                                <button><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i></button>
                            </form>
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-inline-flex auth">
                            <button class="auth-button d-none d-md-block"
                                onclick="window.location = '/login';">Войти</button>
                            <button class="auth-button-mobile d-block d-md-none"
                                onclick="window.location = '/login';"><i
                                    class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-to-bracket"></i></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="topic">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                                <div style="width: 100px;">
                                    <div class="avatar">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-at"></i>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex-column title-subtitle">
                                    <div class="title">
                                        Подтверждение почтового адреса
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="subtitle">
                                        Для завершения регистрации, пожалуйста, подтвердите свой электронный адрес. Ссылка для подтверждения была отправлена на вашу почту. Если вы не видите письмо в вашем почтовом ящике, проверьте папку "Спам" или "Нежелательная почта".
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- footer %>
</body>

</html>